{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "VeriBuy - Metrics & Performance",
    "uid": "veribuy-metrics",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "schemaVersion": 16,
    "version": 1,
    "refresh": "10s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Service Overview",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 3
        },
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "# VeriBuy Metrics & Performance Dashboard\n\nReal-time metrics from all VeriBuy microservices using Prometheus.\n\n**Services Monitored:**\n- ✅ auth-service (3001)\n- ✅ user-service (3002)\n- ✅ listing-service (3003)\n- ⚠️ trust-lens-service (3004) - No metrics endpoint\n- ✅ evidence-service (3006)\n- ✅ transaction-service (3007)\n- ✅ notification-service (3008)\n\n**Metrics Collection:** NestJS PrometheusModule → Prometheus\n\n**What's Tracked:**\n- CPU & Memory usage\n- Node.js event loop lag\n- Heap utilization\n- Process metrics"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Service Health",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 3,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 4
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {
            "values": false,
            "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
          },
          "orientation": "auto",
          "textMode": "auto",
          "colorMode": "value",
          "graphMode": "none",
          "justifyMode": "auto"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {
                    "text": "DOWN",
                    "color": "red"
                  },
                  "1": {
                    "text": "UP",
                    "color": "green"
                  }
                }
              }
            ],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "value": 0,
                  "color": "red"
                },
                {
                  "value": 1,
                  "color": "green"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Memory Usage (MB)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 7,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "process_resident_memory_bytes{job=~\".*-service\"} / 1024 / 1024",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "tooltip": {
            "mode": "multi"
          },
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "list",
            "placement": "bottom"
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            },
            "unit": "decmbytes",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "CPU Usage (seconds)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 7,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(process_cpu_seconds_total{job=~\".*-service\"}[1m])",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "tooltip": {
            "mode": "multi"
          },
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "list",
            "placement": "bottom"
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            },
            "unit": "percentunit",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Node.js Event Loop Lag (ms)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 15,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "nodejs_eventloop_lag_seconds{job=~\".*-service\"} * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "tooltip": {
            "mode": "multi"
          },
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "list",
            "placement": "bottom"
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            },
            "unit": "ms",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            },
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "value": 0,
                  "color": "green"
                },
                {
                  "value": 50,
                  "color": "yellow"
                },
                {
                  "value": 100,
                  "color": "red"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Heap Memory Used (MB)",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 15,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "nodejs_heap_size_used_bytes{job=~\".*-service\"} / 1024 / 1024",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "tooltip": {
            "mode": "multi"
          },
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "list",
            "placement": "bottom"
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            },
            "unit": "decmbytes",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "Process Uptime (hours)",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 23,
          "w": 24,
          "h": 4
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "(time() - process_start_time_seconds{job=~\".*-service\"}) / 3600",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "reduceOptions": {
            "values": false,
            "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
          },
          "orientation": "auto",
          "textMode": "value_and_name",
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "none",
          "justifyMode": "auto"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "h",
            "decimals": 2,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "value": 0,
                  "color": "blue"
                },
                {
                  "value": 1,
                  "color": "green"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "title": "Active Handles",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 0,
          "y": 27,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "nodejs_active_handles{job=~\".*-service\"}",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "tooltip": {
            "mode": "multi"
          },
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "list",
            "placement": "bottom"
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            },
            "unit": "short",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "title": "Active Requests",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {
          "x": 12,
          "y": 27,
          "w": 12,
          "h": 8
        },
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "nodejs_active_requests{job=~\".*-service\"}",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "tooltip": {
            "mode": "multi"
          },
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "list",
            "placement": "bottom"
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "drawStyle": "line",
              "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
              "lineWidth": 2,
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            },
            "unit": "short",
            "color": {
              "mode": "palette-classic"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "overwrite": true
}
